        {
            "title": "「鋼鐵大王」遭撕票︱郭從願最後乘坐七人車被棄曝光  駐菲使館促破案",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"菲律賓「鋼鐵大王」郭從願乘坐的七人車（箭咀示）被棄置街頭的影片曝光。\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/134f9d69b82c17caecf8f5cfd271b87b/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250411/_2025041117410064947.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">菲律賓「鋼鐵大王」郭從願乘坐的七人車（箭咀示）被棄置街頭的影片曝光。</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>有菲律賓「鋼鐵大王」之稱的知名華人郭從願（Anson Que）及其司機慘遭撕票不幸遇害，事件震驚當地華人社區。中國駐菲使館向兩名遇害者表示沉痛哀悼，向家屬表達誠摯慰問，並對兇手予以嚴厲譴責。菲律賓中國商會亦登報譴責綁架虐殺暴行。今日（11日），網上更流出郭從願所乘坐的七人車被棄路邊的畫面。\n\n</p><h2>郭從願中國籍 使館嚴正交涉</h2>\n<p>中國駐菲使館對中國公民在菲律賓遭綁架，表示高度重視，黃溪連大使第一時間作出部署，相關部門全力開展營救工作，指導並協助家屬向菲警方和國內公安部門同步報案，同時要求菲執法部門全力偵辦，安全解救人質。不幸的是，該中國公民同其菲籍司機最終被害。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3445896/\">菲律賓「鋼鐵大王」郭從願遭撕票 家人3付贖金共$2900萬</a></strong>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"菲律賓「鋼鐵大王」郭從願乘坐的七人車（箭咀示）被棄置街頭的影片曝光。X@_jamesJA\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6bddc8209fe678e393f7952be473dede/2025-04/525_50_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        菲律賓「鋼鐵大王」郭從願乘坐的七人車（箭咀示）被棄置街頭的影片曝光。X@_jamesJA\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"郭從願在菲律賓有「鋼鐵大王」之稱。海外頻道\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/dbcf36107e512961a7714ef49ce5c4dd/2025-04/376924a9-422e-4ad2-94e4-d63d4988cf67_jpg.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        郭從願在菲律賓有「鋼鐵大王」之稱。海外頻道\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"菲律賓中國商會登報譴責綁架虐殺暴行。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2da18d752308d63e6523bbb8908919a5/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_14_56_11_1_.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        菲律賓中國商會登報譴責綁架虐殺暴行。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"公開聯署聲明。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b4c2eee0472e05b1a5f3b4e4f9df29d3/2025-04/WhatsApp_Image_2025-04-11_at_14_56_11.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        公開聯署聲明。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"郭從願在菲律賓熱心僑務。菲律賓中國商會\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8ac3888bd3a3f09d51e975e39125d7df/2025-04/tlmy.JPG\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        郭從願在菲律賓熱心僑務。菲律賓中國商會\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"郭從願在菲律賓熱心僑務。福建僑聯\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/2f46374b16ca9c715126d5924be4b4b6/2025-04/19101503mmwe_jpg.jpeg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        郭從願在菲律賓熱心僑務。福建僑聯\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"菲律賓「鋼鐵大王」郭從願，出生於福建永春縣仙夾鎮龍水村。永春縣融媒體\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/af335a3e4e5881eed86767c8a0380f98/2025-04/640_.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        菲律賓「鋼鐵大王」郭從願，出生於福建永春縣仙夾鎮龍水村。永春縣融媒體\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"菲律賓媒體人公開郭從願及其司機的遺照，顯示二人生前疑遭酷刑。拉蒙•圖爾福FB\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/6ac603bb9f6957c9f01fc61e564f1372/2025-04/A_943.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        菲律賓媒體人公開郭從願及其司機的遺照，顯示二人生前疑遭酷刑。拉蒙•圖爾福FB\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"郭從願生前積極回饋家鄉永春縣。永春縣融媒體\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/55722ccc43f4f0099402d356aaee652c/2025-04/52526640.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        郭從願生前積極回饋家鄉永春縣。永春縣融媒體\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>駐菲使館稱，當事人遇害後，使館領導立即向菲有關部門負責人提出嚴正交涉，要求菲方動員一切力量和資源，盡早偵破案件，將兇手繩之以法。針對近期涉中國公民綁架等惡性犯罪持續上升的勢頭，認真傾聽華社呼聲，與菲華主要社團共同商討對策，採取切實措施保護在菲中國公民和華僑華人安全與合法權益。\n\n</p>\n<p><strong>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3445896/\">鋼鐵大王︱郭從願生前疑受酷刑 傳綁匪操普通話或涉租務糾紛</a></strong>\n</p>\n<p>駐菲使館重申，中國政府一貫高度重視保護海外中國公民安全與合法權益，對侵害中國公民的犯罪行為絕不姑息。駐菲使館將繼續敦促菲方加大力度，全力偵破有關案件，嚴懲兇手，嚴格執法，加強治安，還華社安寧。\n\n</p>\n<p>此外，郭從願一案發生後，當地三大商會發表聯合聲明，敦促政府盡快緝捕綁匪，改善治安。目前，菲警方已就該案件成立了特別調查工作組。\n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
